---
const cities = ["MIAMI", "ORLANDO", "CHARLOTTE", "NEW YORK", "BOSTON"];
---

<section class="bg-[#060606] py-16 md:py-24" id="inscribirme">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl rounded-2xl border border-white/20 p-8 md:p-12">
        <h2 class="text-center font-playfair text-3xl font-normal italic text-white md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl">
        Asegura tu cupo
        </h2>

        <p class="mt-4 text-center text-base text-white/70 md:text-lg">
        Asegura tu lugar hoy y entra al c√≠rculo de pioneros en exosomas.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-8 flex justify-center">
        <a
            href="#reservar"
            class="rounded-lg bg-white px-10 py-4 text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-[#060606] transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-[#bfa792] hover:text-white"
        >
            Reservar con 30%
        </a>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-10 space-y-3">
        {cities.map((city) => (
            <a
            href={`#${city.toLowerCase().replace(" ", "-")}`}
            class="block font-playfair text-2xl font-bold italic text-white transition-colors hover:text-[#bfa792] md:text-3xl"
            >
            {city}
            </a>
        ))}
        </div>
    </div>
    </div>
</section>